---
title: Double Herby Pork & Roast Veggie Toss with Chargrilled Capsicum Yoghurt
description: Allow us to take you on a culinary escapade and savour the flavours of the Mediterranean with this delectable dish. Juicy pork is perfectly cooked in our Tuscan herb seasoning, with a drizzle of honey for a touch of sweetness. A medley of roasted veggies and a tangy sauce drizzled over the top complete this perfect meal!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6604f3660d5f299b40db82a5-2f0e59fb.jpeg
